Rory Calhoun https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rory_Calhoun 0 Rory Calhoun (born Francis Timothy McCown, August 8, 1922 – April 28, 1999) was an American film and television actor, screenwriter and producer. He starred in a large number of Westerns in the 1950s and 1960s, and appeared in support parts in films such as How to Marry a Millionaire (1953).
